Legion Power Manager Applet
Version: 1.0.0
UUID: legion-power@moodliszka
Created: 2025-12-22

FEATURES:
- Complete replacement for power@cinnamon.org
- All standard power management features
- Legion-specific controls (Conservation, Rapid Charge, Fan Mode)
- 1007 lines of production-ready JavaScript
- Comprehensive documentation
- Automated installation tools

COMPATIBILITY:
- Cinnamon: 4.x, 5.x, 6.x
- Target: Cinnamon 6.x
- Base: power@cinnamon.org (Cinnamon official applet)

REQUIREMENTS:
- Cinnamon Desktop Environment
- UPower
- cinnamon-settings-daemon
- power-profiles-daemon (optional, for power profiles)
- Legion Power D-Bus service (optional, for Legion features)

